OL,3,CThe impact of "news avoidance" on
OL,4,Cbroadcast news
OL,6,FThey might be reading individual
OL,7,Fpieces which are fair but which only
OL,8,Fone part of a complex story ` say an
OL,9,Farticle which looks solely at the
OL,10,Fplight of an individual family in Gaza.
OL,12,FMore disturbingly, there is simple
OL,13,Ffake news ` lies, deliberate
OL,14,Fmisinformation and conspiracies
OL,15,Fpresented as fact.
OL,17,FIt is all too easy for anyone to be
OL,18,Ftaken in by this poison.
OL,20,FAnd this is where I would argue
OL,21,Fmainstream broadcast news has a vital
OL,22,Fpart to play.
OL,26,@kD@OOUkD@^O]
