OL,3,CThe impact of "news avoidance" on
OL,4,Cbroadcast news
OL,6,FThink of the main news programmes on
OL,7,Fthe public service channels as simple
OL,8,Ftrusted sources of information.
OL,10,FIf they get something wrong or an
OL,11,Findividual item falls short of
OL,12,Faccepted standards, there are
OL,13,Fconsequences.
OL,15,FIs it time to build on the BBC's
OL,16,Frecent "Trust is Earned" campaign to
OL,17,Fmarket individual programmes?
OL,19,FShould public service broadcasters
OL,20,Fwork together to help the public
OL,21,Funderstand the basics of what they do
OL,22,Fand why?
