OL,3,CThe impact of "news avoidance" on
OL,4,Cbroadcast news
OL,6,FBut perhaps there might be glimmers of
OL,7,Fhope.
OL,9,FTV news ratings have fallen in recent
OL,10,Fyears. Apart from the more disturbing
OL,11,Freasons I mentioned, some of this is
OL,12,Fsimply down to multichannel TV and the
OL,13,Fpopularity of streaming.
OL,15,FThe days of Neighbours boosting the
OL,16,Fratings of the One and Six o'Clock
OL,17,FNews seem like something from a
OL,18,Fdistant age.
OL,26,@kD@OOUkD@^O]
