OL,3,CThe impact of "news avoidance" on
OL,4,Cbroadcast news
OL,6,FBut ratings do seem to be stabilising.
OL,7,FLast Monday the 6.30pm regional
OL,8,Fprogrammes on BBC One had 4m viewers `
OL,9,Fthe highest ratings of the day.
OL,11,FThe clocks went back last night, the
OL,12,Fnights are drawing in and the weather
OL,13,Fis getting worse.
OL,15,FTrends are not inevitable ` just as
OL,16,Fthe resurgence of vinyl records and
OL,17,Fthe increase in the use of cash took
OL,18,Fmany by surprise.
