OL,3,CThe impact of "news avoidance" on
OL,4,Cbroadcast news
OL,6,FThere are many who do not engage with
OL,7,Fbroadcast news and it is important for
OL,8,Freputable journalists to try to reach
OL,9,Fthe public on a whole range of
OL,10,Fplatforms.
OL,12,FBut perhaps reports of its impending
OL,13,Fdemise are, in part, wishful thinking
OL,14,Fby those who might see benefit for
OL,15,Fthemselves in a failure to offer fair,
OL,16,Fbalanced and objective news.
